---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'July 15, 2026';
---

<Layout title="Disclaimer" description="Affiliate link disclosure and content accuracy disclaimer for mikemurphy.ai." canonical="/disclaimer/">
  <main class="mm-container py-16">
    <p class="mm-eyebrow">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="mm-h1 mt-3">Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="mm-lede mt-5">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="mm-prose prose mt-8 max-w-3xl">
      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        mikemurphy.ai participates in affiliate programs, including the Amazon
        Associates Program and other affiliate or sponsorship arrangements.
        This means that some links on the Site may be affiliate links — if you
        click one and make a qualifying purchase or sign up for a service, we
        may earn a commission at no additional cost to you.
      </p>
      <p>
        As an Amazon Associate, I earn from qualifying purchases. Affiliate
        relationships do not influence which products, tools, or services are
        covered or how they are described; opinions expressed are my own.
      </p>

      <h2>Sponsored Content</h2>
      <p>
        From time to time, content on the Site or in the AI Unplugged
        newsletter may be sponsored or created in partnership with a company.
        Sponsored content will be clearly labeled as such.
      </p>

      <h2>Accuracy of Content</h2>
      <p>
        Content on this Site — including tutorials, newsletter issues, and
        commentary on AI tools and technology — is provided for informational
        and educational purposes only. AI tools, products, pricing, and
        capabilities change quickly, and information that was accurate when
        published may become outdated. We make reasonable efforts to keep
        content current and accurate but do not guarantee its completeness,
        reliability, or applicability to your specific situation.
      </p>
      <p>
        Nothing on this Site constitutes professional, legal, financial, or
        technical advice. You should independently verify any information
        before relying on it and consult a qualified professional where
        appropriate.
      </p>

      <h2>External Links</h2>
      <p>
        The Site may link to third-party tools, products, or websites for
        convenience or reference. We do not endorse and are not responsible
        for the content, accuracy, or practices of any third-party site.
      </p>

      <h2>No Guarantees</h2>
      <p>
        Any results, outcomes, or examples described on the Site (including
        in tutorials) are illustrative and not guaranteed. Your results may
        vary based on your own tools, setup, and use case.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this Disclaimer can be sent to
        <a href="mailto:mike@mikemurphy.co">mike@mikemurphy.co</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
